# Mylapore Citizen Portal — frontend env reference
#
# Local dev:
#   Leave VITE_API_URL UNSET. The Vite dev server proxies /api → :5050
#   (configured in vite.config.js), so the portal hits the local Express
#   backend automatically.
#
# Production (Vercel):
#   Set VITE_API_URL in the Vercel dashboard:
#     Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#     Key:   VITE_API_URL
#     Value: https://tvk-mla-support.onrender.com/api
#
#   The /portal/* path is appended at every call site, so this value should
#   end at the API root (/api), NOT at /api/portal.
#
# After changing VITE_API_URL on Vercel you MUST redeploy — Vite bakes the
# value into the bundle at build time.
VITE_API_URL=
